You can purchase LITALICO Inc.’s digital contents such as stories, illustrations and items. The Pricing will be shown on the final confirmation screen. You will purchase our application through a store including, but not limited to, Google Inc., iTunes K.K., Amazon.co.jp or Amazon.com. Inc. as prescribed. If you subscribe monthly course, subscriptions renew automatically unless you unsubscribe. If you decide unsubscribe, need to cancel the course. Please note that if automatic withdrawal is done without cancel procedure, automatic charging will be continued. LITALICO Inc. may temporarily, in the form of a campaign, etc., or permanently change the purchase price of content or our service without providing prior notification to user. In this case, LITALICO Inc. will not provide compensation for the difference between the original price nor provide refunds.
