This application will be the possession of the user as soon as it is purchased. When purchasing content, you will be charged communication fee additionally. Regarding payments, LITALICO Inc. will not be liable for any dispute between the purchaser such as  Google Inc. ,iTunes K.K., Amazon.co.jp or Amazon.com.Inc. and the matter should be resolved between them. Minors must receive permission from adults to purchase content. If you uninstall this application before receiving purchased content, you will need to contact us to get content. LITALICO Inc. will not be liable to refund because of the lateness of providing content to user.
3. Prohibited acts
Purchaser of this content may not exchange content with cash. You agree to pay all fees and applicable taxes incurred by you or anyone using an Account registered to you. Unless specifically indicated otherwise, you may not use our application for profit-making or commercial purposes, you may not cause act to interfere any third party, our service or violate applicable laws.
