If you fail to pay charges even after the payment due date has passed, fail to comply with any of the terms and conditions and laws, commit any other wrongful act, LITALICO Inc. may discontinue your usage of the applications.You acknowledge that LITALICO Inc. is not required to provide a refund for any reason, and that you will not receive money or other compensation when an account it closed, whether such closure was voluntary or involuntary.
5. Refund
You acknowledge that LITALICO Inc. is not required to provide a refund for any reason other than accordance with the laws. If refund occurs by law, LITALICO Inc. will make a public announcement through its homepage and procedure will be made as ruled by laws.
